Package: esq.handsontable
Title: Interactive Data Tables with 'Handsontable' for 'shiny'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anastasia", "Kostiv", email = "anastasiia.kostiv.ext@esqlabs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides an interactive, Excel-like data table input for 'shiny'
    applications. Wraps 'Handsontable' <https://handsontable.com/> and 'React'
    to offer editable tables with dropdown columns, multi-select with sorting,
    validation, conditional cell disabling, context menu, and dynamic option
    updates at runtime.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/esqlabs/esq.handsontable
BugReports: https://github.com/esqlabs/esq.handsontable/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
